Description: =======================
        Init Flask Restful Api
        =======================
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/jenkins/build?jobUrl=http%3A%2F%2F120.24.219.111%3A9000%2Fjob%2Frflask   :alt: Jenkins
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/rflask   :alt: PyPI
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/wheel/rflask   :alt: PyPI - Wheel
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/rflask   :alt: PyPI - License
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/dd/rflask   :alt: PyPI - Downloads
        
        ------------
        Installing
        ------------
        
        Install and update using `pip`_:
        
        .. code-block:: text
        
            pip install -U rflask
        
        -------------------
        A Simple Example
        -------------------
        
        .. code-block:: text
        
            $ rflask init
            project_name: [flask-restful-api-20200125-090404]
            author: [Deacon]
            author_email: [deacon@example.com]
            description: [Flask restful api project.]
            ...
            ...
            Create file /Users/donghp/Downloads/Git_doc/PythonProject/init-flask-restful-api/flask-restful-api-20200125-090404/supervisord_example.conf
        
            Done.
        
        **Project dir tree**:
        
        .. code-block:: text
        
            .
            ├── applications
            │   ├── test
            │   │   ├── README.rst
            │   │   ├── __init__.py
