            2020-01-23 13:03:24,604 [4616764864:MainThread] [_internal.py:_internal:_log] [INFO]:  * Debugger PIN: 186-303-110
        
        -------------------
        Deploy to docker
        -------------------
        
        In your project root dir, open the terminal:
        
        .. code-block:: text
        
            $ git clone ***.git
            $ cd <your_project>
            $ docker-compose up
        
